        <div class="cfm-item"><strong>Filter restriction</strong><span>A dirty filter reduces effective CFM by 30–50% regardless of motor power</span></div>
        <div class="cfm-item"><strong>Our assessment</strong><span>We evaluate CFM rating and duct sizing on every pro-range hood call</span></div>
